OL,3,CTeen to stand trial after denying
OL,4,Ckilling woman on night out
OL,6,FA 19-year-old has denied killing a
OL,7,Fwoman who died following an alleged
OL,8,Faltercation near a bar.
OL,10,FLiam Moor appeared at Newcastle Crown
OL,11,FCourt to deny the manslaughter of Lisa
OL,12,FDenton, 40, who died in hospital
OL,13,Ffollowing an incident in North
OL,14,FShields, North Tyneside, on 24 January.
OL,16,FNorthumbria Police previously said she
OL,17,Fsuffered a serious head injury on the
OL,18,Fnight and died the following morning.
