OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1772447793
OL,3,CTeen to stand trial after denying
OL,4,Ckilling woman on night out
OL,6,FMoor, of no fixed address, was granted
OL,7,Fbail and will go on trial on 14
OL,8,FSeptember.
OL,10,FAfter she died, Ms Denton's family
OL,11,Fsaid: "Lisa was the kind of person
OL,12,Fwhose personality truly shone warm,
OL,13,Fgenuine, and full of life, with a dry
OL,14,Fsense of humour that could catch you
OL,15,Foff guard and leave you smiling long
OL,16,Fafter.
OL,18,F"She had a way of making people feel
OL,19,Fseen and welcomed, whether they were
OL,20,Flifelong friends or someone she'd just
OL,21,Fmet."
